{
  "stem": "26672.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, he came to the place of work where I work to ask if I seen anybody-- didn't accuse me-- if I'd seen it, because he never thought that I would ever be able of doing that such a thing.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did I see anybody go into the barracks?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said-- of course, I said, I didn't see anyone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just told me not to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He asked did I go to the barracks, did I clean his room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, no, you told me you were going away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was hit by the capo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was hit so hard for being accused, or even asked by a German, did I see anybody?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did I do anything, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So therefore, the capo gave me a good hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But within a day or so, and we-- we weren't allowed to go out anymore to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the group escaped, and I was right behind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And what nationality was the capo?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He must have been Polish Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most capos were Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tschenstochau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Tschenstochau was already under SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as we got off the trains, there was a guy with a little-- with a stick, pointing which way to go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- there's a lot of children came from that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he selected the grownups on one side and children other side And he obviously, he could see I wasn't a grownup, and so he pushed me, and he told me to come with the children.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went and laid in front of him, kneeled in front of him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I'm a man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, ask anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was working at the other camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm 15.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just happened to push me away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By pushing me away, he pushed me among the grownups.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
